name: Yaasmyn Fula - The Untold Story of Tupac Amaru Shakur & Yaki Kadafi Fula

metadata.title: Flash Mints (Yaasmyn Fula - Genesis Drop) #1
metadata.description: Introducing Yaasmyn Fula's 1st complete NFT collection: Composed of 1,004 unique NFT editions of Yaasmyn Fula's photographs (Each NFT is numbered with a serial number proving its authenticity). This collection represents a portion of Yaasmyn Fula’s private collection of photos that he’s shot from over the years. Each NFT tells a story from Yaasmyn Fula's perspective about the shot and unlocks exclusive benefits, rewards, and surprises for all NFT holders of this collection.
